Teak wood and charcoal canvas directors chair. Combine flexibility and style with the Skagerak Junction Chair. Seagrass has natural color variations which makes every basket unique. Inspired by classic directors chairs, this timelessly stylish canvas chair is specifically developed for outdoor use.
Weather-resistant with a completely foldable teak wood frame, Junction is the perfect space-saver for modest patios and balcony settings.

